Fries ~ Korean Fried Cauliflower ~ Family Shiitake Mushroom Shawarma
RATING_COMMENT:
Firstly, the food is incredibly tasty. The shiitake is scrumptious, the korean cauliflower is delicious and the fries are perfect!! 
There was 2 family of 4's here yesterday for a movie night. We ordered 2 shiitake family meals, so it should have fed 8 people.
however, for a "family of 4" the shitake only provided us with 4 schwarma wraps, with very little filling. We had to use the fries to fill in the rest. The pickled onions were delicious added in. we had left over flatbread and no shiitake to fill it.
I've ordered before and got a single portion of shiitake. The family size looked like double the single, which would be for 2 people and not 4. If it was just me and my partner, it would have been plenty. 
Both families were still left hungry so we had to cook up some fries an hour later as no one was full. 

again, food is delicious but portions aren't great. If I order again, it'll be when it's just me and my partner.

This different pickles in the salad were really tasty too. Also, having a choice of tzatziki and hummus was great as this catered for us all. I will definitely be back for more.
